### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8007/health

### 创建人格
POST http://localhost:8007/persona/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "u1",
  "persona_id": "default",
  "display_name": "Ava",
  "description": "Primary persona"
}

### 追加消息
POST http://localhost:8007/messages/append
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "u1",
  "persona_id": "default",
  "session_id": "s1",
  "source_app": "cli",
  "role": "user",
  "content": "Hello there"
}

### 写入记忆
POST http://localhost:8007/memory/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "u1",
  "persona_id": "default",
  "type": "preferences",
  "key": "tone",
  "content": "Short, friendly responses"
}

### 召回
POST http://localhost:8007/memory/recall
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "u1",
  "persona_id": "default",
  "query": "friendly"
}
